eu_initiatives:
We actively take part in Horizon 2020 and EU health program with a focus on: 
- evaluation of the cost-effectiveness of healthcare innovations, incl. eHealth, medtech, new care models for people with chronic disease(s) and elders, drugs; 
- evaluation of the implementation and scaling-up of healthcare innovations, incl. eHealth, medtech, new care models for people with chronic disease(s) and elders, drugs.
